comments: Zizic (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Connaughton (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bledsoe (MIL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Middleton (MIL) slightly extends his arm at the end of the drive but Osman's (CLE) momentum is carrying him towards the basket when the marginal contact occurs.
Lopez (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Clarkson (CLE).
Bledsoe (MIL) makes slight contact with Sexton (CLE) as he gathers during his driving shot attempt but he does not extend his forearm out and dislodge Sexton.
Nance Jr. (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bledsoe (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ilyasova (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Sexton (CLE).
Bledsoe (MIL) and Sexton (CLE) engage and separate off ball during the inbound.
Sexton (CLE) makes contact to Bledsoe's (MIL) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Nance Jr. (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bledsoe (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bledsoe (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position on Sexton (CLE) at the end of the drive.
Middleton (MIL) makes incidental contact to Osman's (CLE) off-arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Ilyasova (MIL) makes marginal contact to the midsection of Nance Jr. (CLE) but does not affect his ability to get the rebound.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Nwaba (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bledsoe (MIL) commits a take foul on Clarkson (CLE).
Connaughton (MIL) commits a take foul on Clarkson (CLE).
Nance Jr. (CLE) legally goes after the loose ball when Bledsoe (MIL) loses control of his dribble.
